{
    "_comment": "Cosmos-Reason2-8B via hosted API endpoint (e.g. Lepton). No GPU required. Set env vars: COSMOS_REASON2_API_BASE (full endpoint URL) and COSMOS_API_KEY or NVIDIA_API_KEY. Requires: pip install qwen-vl-utils and ffmpeg on PATH.",
